00:00:05.651 --> 00:00:07.987 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Mephibosheth

00:00:07.987 --> 00:00:10.656 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
â€”his grandfather had tried to kill David.

00:00:12.074 --> 00:00:14.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When David became king and asked

00:00:14.201 --> 00:00:15.870 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Mephibosheth to the palace,

00:00:15.870 --> 00:00:17.371 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
