00:00:28.757 --> 00:00:31.260 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Here is your servant.

00:00:31.260 --> 00:00:32.678 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Mephibosheth,

00:00:35.347 --> 00:00:37.892 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
do not be afraid,

00:00:37.892 --> 00:00:40.477 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for I will certainly show loyal love to you

00:00:40.477 --> 00:00:42.730 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for the sake of your father Jonathan,

00:00:43.981 --> 00:00:45.983 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I will return to you

00:00:45.983 --> 00:00:47.860 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
