00:00:50.988 --> 00:00:53.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And you will always dine at my table.

00:00:59.580 --> 00:01:01.707 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What is your servant,

00:01:01.707 --> 00:01:04.168 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that you have turned your attention

00:01:04.168 --> 00:01:06.587 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
